actions.command: /execute as @a[tag=foxie,distance=..5] run title @s actionbar {"text": "Figura avatar mode ON, your hitbox and eye height is shrink according to the fox avatar","color":"aqua"}

/power revoke @a[tag=foxie] thorigins:fox/universal_settings thorigins:universal
